{"tid":1545263,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[終極和理非請入] 仆你個街大公報依家周街派呀","createTime":"2019-09-06T00:38:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T15:55:36.000Z","uid":89063,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d2d04100b7c15c769fb58f2a2b857154eda22a42","tid":1545263,"uid":89063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T00:38:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">TLDR<br />\n唔該喺條街道見倒有免費派大公報就係咁攞<br />\n幫自己啲親朋戚友、同事一人攞一份<br />\n每少一份就少一個盲毛睇大公報！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家有冇發現近依幾年開始有份「大公報精華版」喺條街道見人就派<br />\n近依幾個月唔知係咪有加印，好似派極都派唔完咁<br />\n我見倒啱啱樓下公園啲呀伯一人揸住一份大公報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔該為咗毫無成本地拯救老一輩，避免佢哋成為廢老，請大家見倒就狗衝過去攞一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da26d6baa9300ab3d1423eed64695746eca2b4e2","tid":1545263,"uid":89063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T00:38:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">你可能會問：免費版係咪對腦部傷害冇咁大？</span><br />\n我可以好肯定咁同你講，唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b70a326ff39aef2eea2a0e417d53670ba3ce7ebb","tid":1545263,"uid":89063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T00:39:22.000Z","msg":"我愛大公報1<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"769f7891d30a42d9fda2161fba43a607369d880e","tid":1545263,"uid":89063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T00:39:32.000Z","msg":"我愛大公報2<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ab7c0c12c97a329f916eaaba1501c3052d027fa","tid":1545263